## Writing Good Policies

```json
// Too permissive — do not do this
{
  "Effect": "Allow",
  "Action": "s3:*",
  "Resource": "*"
}

// Least privilege — do this
{
  "Effect": "Allow",
  "Action": ["s3:GetObject", "s3:PutObject"],
  "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::my-app-bucket/uploads/*"
}

// With condition — restrict to specific IP range
{
  "Effect": "Allow",
  "Action": "s3:GetObject",
  "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::my-app-bucket/*",
  "Condition": {
    "IpAddress": {
      "aws:SourceIp": ["203.0.113.0/24"]
    }
  }
}
```

