## Policy Simulator

Test policies before applying them:

```bash
# Simulate whether a user can perform an action
aws iam simulate-principal-policy \
  --policy-source-arn arn:aws:iam::ACCOUNT_ID:user/joon-dev \
  --action-names s3:GetObject \
  --resource-arns arn:aws:s3:::my-app-bucket/file.txt
```

Or use the IAM Policy Simulator in the console — it is one of the most useful debugging tools in AWS.

