## Common Managed Policies

```
arn:aws:iam::aws:policy/ReadOnlyAccess            → read everything, change nothing
arn:aws:iam::aws:policy/AmazonS3FullAccess        → full S3
arn:aws:iam::aws:policy/AmazonEC2ReadOnlyAccess   → read EC2
arn:aws:iam::aws:policy/AmazonEKSClusterPolicy    → EKS cluster operations
arn:aws:iam::aws:policy/AmazonEKSWorkerNodePolicy → EKS node group
arn:aws:iam::aws:policy/CloudWatchAgentServerPolicy → CloudWatch agent on EC2
```

